snippet.title: The Sims 3 Movie Stuff Trailer -- Part 2
snippet.description: Set the stage with The Sims 3 Movie Stuff and tell more unique stories with décor, furnishings, and clothing inspired by iconic movie genres. Furnish your Sims' homes with cheeky horror décor and dress them in playfully horrific costume. Cast your Sims in The Sims 3 Movie Stuff.
